B Communications Buys Additional Bezeq Shares, Calcalist Says

-- B y   C a l e v   B e n - D a v i d
-- 
2011-03-10T14:30:44Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-10/b-communications-buys-additional-bezeq-shares-calcalist-says.html
B Communications Ltd. purchased an
additional 150 million shekels worth of shares in Bezeq Israeli
Telecommunication Corp., Calcalist reported, without saying how
it obtained the information.   B Communications held a 30 percent stake in Bezeq prior to
the purchase, Calcalist said. Spokesmen for B Communications and
Bezeq were not immediately available for comment.   Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
